    <%# -----------DIV PROJECT GRINGO INIT----------%>
    <div class="projects-gringo" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500" data-controller="project">
      <div class="projects-text">
        <h3>Grin.go</h3>
        <p>Connection platform between travelers and locals</p>
        <p>Grin.go is our final project for the course and the most challenging one. Within this project, we worked with JS, Rails, Ruby, CSS, WebSocket, and MVC. The platform was deployed on Heroku, and the entire front-end layout was created using Figma. We developed a real-time chat where two individuals could converse and plan trips. The platform's idea is to connect travelers with locals, providing an enhanced experience for both the traveler and the host.</p>
        <%= link_to "Click here to see the code", "https://github.com/victorgqueiroz/Grin.go", class: "links" %>
      </div>
