      <div class="projects-text">
        <h3>RoastHub</h3>
        <p>A Hub for specialty coffee sales</p>
        <p>RoastHub is designed for coffee enthusiasts who never seem to find a platform that truly provides all the information they seek. Here, we strive to bring everything specialty coffee has to offer closer to the consumer. The platform was developed using JS, CSS, Ruby, and Rails. We also employed MVC for the construction process. The entire front-end was previously designed in Figma.</p>
